        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Anti-Terrorism Act of 2011 - Bars a federal agency from prohibiting an airline pilot, copilot, or navigator, or law enforcement person specifically detailed for protection of an aircraft from carrying a firearm.</p>]]></text>
